    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes extensions to Border Gateway Protocol (BGP)
   for distributing a Bit Index Explicit Replication Traffic/Tree
   Engineering (BIER-TE) path.  A new Tunnel Type for BIER-TE path is
   defined to encode the information about a BIER-TE path.</t>
